<h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<div class="faq" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;">
  <details style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--muted); border-radius: var(--radius); cursor: pointer;">
    <summary style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--foreground); user-select: none;">Is the 3D Moon Lamp safe to use?</summary>
    <div style="margin-top: 1rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.6;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">Absolutely safe. USB power is inherently low voltage (5V) and safe for all rooms, including children's bedrooms. The LED generates minimal heat—it stays cool even after hours of continuous use. No fire risk, no overheating. Just keep away from water and extreme heat. Safe for all ages and spaces.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--muted); border-radius: var(--radius); cursor: pointer;">
    <summary style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--foreground); user-select: none;">What's the difference between 2-color and 16-color variants?</summary>
    <div style="margin-top: 1rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.6;">
      <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>2-Color Manual:</strong> Warm white and warm yellow only. Toggle with a single button on the base. Simpler, cheaper, great for minimalists who want one consistent look. No learning curve.</p>
      <p style="margin: 1rem 0 0 0;"><strong>16-Color Remote:</strong> Full color spectrum plus brightness control (0–100%), timer options (off, 1hr, 3hrs, 8hrs, always on), and memory function to save your favorite color. Requires the included remote control. More versatile for those who like to experiment with different moods.</p>
      <p style="margin: 1rem 0 0 0;">Choose 2-color for simplicity and budget. Choose 16-color if you want flexibility and don't mind slightly higher price.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--muted); border-radius: var(--radius); cursor: pointer;">
    <summary style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--foreground); user-select: none;">How long does the LED last?</summary>
    <div style="margin-top: 1rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.6;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">The LED has a rated lifespan of 10,000+ hours. At 8 hours per day, that's over 3.4 years of continuous nightly use before needing replacement. In reality, the LED will likely outlast the PLA plastic material's lifespan. You're probably looking at 5+ years of practical use.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--muted); border-radius: var(--radius); cursor: pointer;">
