      <p style="margin: 0.75rem 0;"><strong>20cm:</strong> Large showpiece. Room centerpiece. Dramatic visual impact. Requires substantial surface area.</p>
      <p style="margin: 0.75rem 0 0 0;">Larger sizes have more dramatic crater detail visibility and create more impressive ambiance. Smaller sizes are more versatile in tight spaces.</p>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details style="padding: 1rem; background: var(--muted); border-radius: var(--radius); cursor: pointer;">
    <summary style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--foreground); user-select: none;">Does it work as a primary night light?</summary>
