      <p style="margin: 0;">Yes, absolutely. The moon lamp emits enough soft glow for safe navigation in dark rooms and hallways. Perfect for nighttime bathroom trips or kids' rooms. The 16-color remote variant includes timer modes (1hr, 3hrs, 8hrs) if you want it to auto-off after you fall asleep. Gentle, non-jarring light that won't disrupt sleep cycles like bright white LEDs.</p>
